        "copyright": "Aurora over Spirit Island on Maligne Lake, Jasper National Park, Alberta, Canada (© Mumemories/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Maligne+Lake+Canada&form=hpcapt",
