            "ImageContent": {
                "Description": "Chapada Diamantina is a natural beauty that seems to have emerged straight from a dream. Established in 1985, Chapada Diamantina National Park in Brazil celebrates 40 years of preservation this year. Located in the heart of the state of Bahia, the park is one of the most impressive ecotourism destinations, covering approximately 152,000 hectares of inspiring landscapes.",
