        "copyright": "Waterfall at Wimbachklamm Gorge, Bavaria, Germany (© EyeEm Mobile GmbH/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Wimbachklamm&form=hpcapt",
