        "copyright": "Autumn colours below Mount Sneffels near Ridgway, Colorado, United States (© Grant Ordelheide/TANDEM Stills + Motion)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mount+Sneffels&form=hpcapt",
