        "copyright": "A female Eurasian red squirrel carrying moss, Switzerland (© Jean-Luc and Francoise Ziegler/Minden Pictures)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Eurasian+red+squirrel&form=hpcapt",
        "title": "Info",
        "quiz": "/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz&filters=WQOskey:%22HPQuiz_20250909_SwissSquirrel%22&FORM=HPQUIZ",
