        "copyright": "Mangrove trees at twilight, Walakiri Beach, island of Sumba, Indonesia (© Boonchet Ch./Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mangrove&form=hpcapt",
        "title": "Info",
        "quiz": "/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz&filters=WQOskey:%22HPQuiz_20250726_MangroveTwilight%22&FORM=HPQUIZ",
